ode/1239 |title=Demon FM Meets....Patrick Melton |website=[[Demon FM]] |host=[[Patrick Melton]], Matt Horn and David Murphy |date=July 14, 2010 |accessdate=July 14, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5rTaohACn?url=http://www.demonfm.co.uk/?q=node%2F1239 |archivedate=July 25, 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"demonFM3\">{{cite podcast |url=http://www.demonfm.co.uk/?q=node/1417 |title=Demon FM Meets....Kevin Greutert (Saw 3D) |website=Demon FM |host=[[Kevin Greutert]] and Matt Horn |date=September 15, 2010 |accessdate=September 16, 2010 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716022059/http://www.demonfm.co.uk/?q=node%2F1417 |archivedate=July 16, 2011 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<!--<ref name=\"demonFM4\">{{cite video|url=http://www.demonfm.co.uk/?q=node/1449|title=Demon FM Meets....Devon Bostick|medium=podcast|publisher=Demon FM|people=[[Devon Bostick]], David Murphy and Matt Horn |date=September 30, 2010 | accessdate=October 1, 2010|time=11:15\u201311:55}}</ref>-->\n\n<ref name=\"bd5\">{{cite news|url=https://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/19015 |title=Will 'Saw VII 3D' Carry the Moniker 'Endgame' & Conclude the Franchise? |work=Bloody Disgusting |publisher=The Collective |last=Miska |first=Brad |date=February 8, 2010 |accessdate=May 8, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5qwN72cFu?url=http://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/19015 |archivedate=July 3, 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Greutert director\">{{cite news\n |url=https://www.deadline.com/hollywood/saw-vs-paranormal-activity-war-gets-bloody-for-halloween-2010-box-office/ \n |title='Saw 3D' vs 'Paranormal Activity 2' Battle Gets Bloody For Halloween 2010 Box Office \n |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] \n |publisher=[[Mail.com Media]] \n |last=Fleming \n |first=Mike \n |date=January 25, 2010 \n |accessdate=January 26, 2010 \n |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5n5IFefwQ?url=http://www.deadline.com/hollywood/saw-vs-paranormal-activity-war-gets-bloody-for-hallow