' Battle Gets Bloody For Halloween 2010 Box Office \n |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] \n |publisher=[[Mail.com Media]] \n |last=Fleming \n |first=Mike \n |date=January 25, 2010 \n |accessdate=January 26, 2010 \n |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5n5IFefwQ?url=http://www.deadline.com/hollywood/saw-vs-paranormal-activity-war-gets-bloody-for-halloween-2010-box-office/ \n |archivedate=January 27, 2010 \n |url-status=live \n}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"bd6\">{{cite news|url=https://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/18838 |title=OMFG #2: Lionsgate Throws Violent Blow at Paramount: 'Saw' vs 'Paranormal Activity'... IT'S ON! |work=Bloody Disgusting |publisher=The Collective |last=Miska |first=Brad |date=January 26, 2010 |accessdate=January 26, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5n5NAQAxi?url=http://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/18838 |archivedate=January 27, 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LAtimes\">{{cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/07/lionsgate-moves-saw-3d-release-date-to-avoid-face-off-with-paranormal-activity-2.html |title=Lionsgate moves 'Saw 3D' release date to avoid face off with 'Paranormal Activity 2' |last=Fritz |first=Ben |work=[[Los Angeles Times]] |publisher=[[Tribune Company]] |date=July 22, 2010 |accessdate=July 27, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5rY8xWfyt?url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/07/lionsgate-moves-saw-3d-release-date-to-avoid-face-off-with-paranormal-activity-2.html |archivedate=July 28, 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Patrick Melton Talks The Collector 2\">{{cite news|url=https://www.dreadcentral.com/news/36388/exclusive-patrick-melton-talks-the-collector-2-saw-vii-3d-and-more |title=Exclusive: Patrick Melton Talks The Collector 2, Saw VII 3D, and More |work=Dread Central |publisher=CraveOnline Media |last=Decker |first=Sean |date=March 12, 2010 |accessdate=March 12, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5oBp6qesg?url=http://www.dreadcentral.com/news/36388/exclusive-patrick-melton-talks-the-collector-2-saw-vii-3d-and-more |archivedate=March 13, 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"twitter\">{{cite web|url=https://www.twitter.com/davidhackl/status/6763360783 |title=SAW VII 3D sets are going up, casting has begun and I'm waking up at 4AM every day. Yup, we're making a movie. |date=December 17, 2009 |work=[[Twitter]] |publisher=[[David Hackl]] |accessdate=February 9, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nQAhwkLx?url=http://twitter.com/davidhackl/status/6763360783 |archivedate=February 9, 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"TFTO list\">{{cite web|url=http://www.toronto.ca/tfto/pdf/currentlist.pdf |title=Toronto Film & Television Office Current List |format=PDF |work=Toronto Film & Television Office |publisher=Toronto.ca |date=February 22, 2010 |accessdate=February 27, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nrhEklM3?url=http://www.toronto.ca/tfto/pdf/currentlist.pdf |archivedate=February 27, 2010 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ElwesInterview\">{{cite news|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/01/28/cary-elwes-tries-to-open-up-about-saw-3d-on-blu-ray/ |title=Cary Elwes Tries to Open Up About 'Saw 3D' on Blu-ray |last=Gilchrist |first=Todd |work=[[The Wall Street Journal]] |publisher=[[Dow Jones & Company]] |date=January 28, 2011 |accessdate=February 1, 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/61ktvqygI?url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/01/28/cary-elwes-tries-to-open-up-about-saw-3d-on-blu-ray/ |archivedate=September 17, 2011 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Scream Queens\">{{cite news|url=http://blog.vh1.com/2010-09-27/the-celebreality-interview-gabby/#more-145026 |publisher=[[VH1]] |title=The Celebreality Interview: Gabby |date=September 27, 2010 |accessdate=September 27, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5t4b5uTKK?url=http://blog.vh1.com/2010-09-27/the-celebreality-interview-gabby/ |archivedate=September 28, 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\