rst=Wesley |authorlink=Wesley Morris |work=[[The Boston Globe]] |publisher=[[The New York Times Company]] |date=October 30, 2010 |accessdate=November 1, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5u2EGf8Zf?url=http://www.boston.com/ae/movies/articles/2010/10/30/in_its_seventh_and_perhaps_final_chapter_saw_is_a_dull_3_d_disaster/ |archivedate=November 6, 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"TorontoStarOct30\">{{cite news|url=https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/article/883545--saw-3d-a-slight-cut-above |title=Saw 3D: a slight cut above |last=Anderson |first=Jason |work=[[Toronto Star]] |publisher=[[Star Media Group]] |date=October 30, 2010 |accessdate=November 3, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5u2ELNdmJ?url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/article/883545--saw-3d-a-slight-cut-above |archivedate=November 6, 2010 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"home media\">{{cite news|url=http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/topnews.php?id=17388 |title=Saw 3D DVD, Blu Release Title, Cover Art & Details |work=ShockTilYouDrop |publisher=CraveOnline Media |date=December 6, 2010 |accessdate=December 6, 2010 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/61kwNHSpS?url=http://www.shocktillyoudrop.com/news/topnews.php?id=17388 |archivedate=September 17, 2011 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RadioTimes\">{{cite web|last=Jones |first=Alan |url=http://www.radiotimes.com/film/ch8pr/saw-3d-%282010%29 |title=Saw 3D film review |work=[[Radio Times]] |publisher=[[BBC Magazines]] |accessdate=March 3, 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/61l7PmDg8?url=http://www.radiotimes.com/film/ch8pr/saw-3d-(2010) |archivedate=September 17, 2011 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BOM International\">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=saw7.htm|title=Saw 3D (2010) \u2013 International Box Office|work=[[Box Office Mojo]]|publisher=[[Amazon.com]]|accessdate=February 7, 2011}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==External links==\n{{wikiquote}}