{"title_page": "Glenn Dani\u00ebls", "text_new": "{{Short description|Belgian soccer player}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name= Glenn Dani\u00ebls\n|fullname=\n|birth_date= 30 January 1994\n|birth_place= [[Belgium]]\n|position= [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]]\n|years1= \n|clubs1= [[Birmingham City F.C.]]\n|caps1= 0\n|goals1= 0\n|years2= 201x-2013\n|clubs2= [[Celtic F.C.]]<ref>[https://videocelts.com/galleries/celtic-next-gen-series-20112012/ Celtic Next Gen Series 2011/2012] videocelts.com</ref>\n|caps2= 0\n|goals2= 0\n|years3=  2012-2013<ref>[https://www.glasgowtimes.co.uk/sport/13255901.archie-moves-to-strengthen-jags-with-new-keeper/ Archie moves to strengthen Jags with new keeper] Glasgow Times</ref>\n|clubs3= [[Partick Thistle F.C.]]\u2192(''loan'')<ref>[https://videocelts.com/2013/01/blogs/loan-celts/keeper-moves-out-on-loan/ Glenn Daniels moves on loan to Partick Thistle] videocelts.com</ref>\n|caps3= 1\n|goals3= 0\n|years4= 2013-2016<ref name=\"fortuna\">[https://www.fortuna-online.nl/update-oud-fortunezen/ Update Oud-Fortunezen] Fortuna Online</ref>\n|clubs4= [[Fortuna Sittard]]<ref>[https://www.fortuna-online.nl/glenn-daniels-tekent-bij-fortuna/ Glenn Daniels tekent bij Fortuna] FOrtuna Online</ref><ref>[https://www.fortuna-online.nl/glenn-daniels-tekent-bij/ Glenn Daniels tekent bij] Fortuna Online</ref><ref>[https://www.fortuna-online.nl/glenn-daniels-op-proef/ Glenn Daniels op proef] Fortuna Online</ref>\n|caps4= 1\n|goals4= 0\n|years5= 2016-2017\n|clubs5= [[Sporting Hasselt]]<ref name=\"fortuna\"/>\n|caps5= 17\n|goals5= 0\n|years6= 2017-2019<ref>[https://www.voetbalbelgie.be/voetbalnieuws/tien-spelers-verlaten-lommel-sk-deze-zomer/2019/05/02/ Tien spelers verlaten Lommel SK deze zomer] Voetbalbelgie.be</ref>\n|clubs6= [[Lommel S.K.]]<ref>[https://www.internetgazet.be/lommel/geoffrey-ket-en-glenn-daniels-naar-lommel-sk.aspx Jeffrey Ket en Glenn Dani\u00ebls naar Lommel SK] Internetgazet</ref>\n|caps6= 2\n|goals6= 0\n}}\n\n'''Glenn Daniels''' (born 30 January 1994 in [[Belgium]]) is a [[Belgium|Belgian]] footballer who is last known to have played for [[Lommel S.K.]] in his home country.\n\n==Career==\n\nDaniels started his senior career with [[Birmingham City F.C.|Birmingham City]]. In 2012, he signed for [[Partick Thistle F.C.|Partick Thistle]] in the [[Scottish Championship]], where he made one appearance and scored zero goals.<ref>[https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=68876 Soccer Base Profile]</ref> After that, he played for Dutch club [[Fortuna Sittard]] and Belgian clubs [[Sporting Hasselt]] and [[Lommel S.K.]] before retiring. \n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://www.glasgowtimes.co.uk/sport/13247379.jags-daniels-looks-to-be-monarch-of-the-sfl-glenn/ Jags' Daniels looks to be monarch of the SFL Glenn] \n* [https://www.glasgowtimes.co.uk/sport/13255700.glenns-content-with-waiting-game/ Glenn's content with waiting game] \n* [https://www.questia.com/article/1G1-315291664/i-ve-learned-from-best-2-in-the-world I've Learned from Best 2 in the World] \n* [https://www.fortunasc.nl/behind-the-scenes-glenn-danials/ Glenn Dani\u00ebls (ex-Birmingham en Celtic): \u2018Opleidingsvergoeding was molensteen rond mijn hals\u2019 (full article)]\n* [https://www.standaard.be/cnt/dmf20141118_01383761 Glenn Dani\u00ebls (ex-Birmingham en Celtic): \u2018Opleidingsvergoeding was molensteen rond mijn hals\u2019] \n* [https://www.google.com/search?rlz=1CARWXF_enUS884&biw=1366&bih=609&ei=pbUgXv2fC67K0PEP4KG60Ak&q=Glenn+Dani%C3%ABls+doelman+site%3Anieuwsblad.be&oq=Glenn+Dani%C3%ABls+doelman+site%3Anieuwsblad.be&gs_l=psy-ab.3...2542.4846..5097...0.0..0.123.1358.16j2......0....1..gws-wiz.9t9xIwHhE-k&ved=0ahUKEwi9hr_d6YjnAhUuJTQIHeCQDpoQ4dUDCAs&uact=5&safe=active&ssui=on Het Nieuwsblad Tag] \n* [https://videocelts.com/2013/06/blogs/former-celts/keepers-belgian-move/ Glenn Daniels on trial at Genk] \n* [https://nl.soccerway.com/players/glenn-daniels/265491/ at Soccerway] \n* [https://www.fortunasc.nl/glenn-danials/ Fortuna Supporters collectief Profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Dani\u00ebls, Glenn}}\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n\n{{soccer-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Short description|Belgian soccer player}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n|name= Glenn Dani\u00ebls\n|fullname=\n|birth_date= 30 January 1994\n|birth_place= [[Belgium]]\n|position= [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]]\n|years1= \n|clubs1= [[Birmingham City F.C.]]\n|caps1= 0\n|goals1= 0\n|years2= 201x-2013\n|clubs2= [[Celtic F.C.]]<ref>[https://videocelts.com/galleries/celtic-next-gen-series-20112012/ Celtic Next Gen Series 2011/2012] videocelts.com</ref>\n|caps2= 0\n|goals2= 0\n|years3=  2012-2013<ref>[https://www.glasgowtimes.co.uk/sport/13255901.archie-moves-to-strengthen-jags-with-new-keeper/ Archie moves to strengthen Jags with new keeper] Glasgow Times</ref>\n|clubs3= [[Partick Thistle F.C.]]\u2192(''loan'')<ref>[https://videocelts.com/2013/01/blogs/loan-celts/keeper-moves-out-on-loan/ Glenn Daniels moves on loan to Partick Thistle] videocelts.com</ref>\n|caps3= 1\n|goals3= 0\n|years4= 2013-2016<ref name=\"fortuna\">[https://www.fortuna-online.nl/update-oud-fortunezen/ Update Oud-Fortunezen] Fortuna Online</ref>\n|clubs4= [[Fortuna Sittard]]<ref>[https://www.fortuna-online.nl/glenn-daniels-tekent-bij-fortuna/ Glenn Daniels tekent bij Fortuna] FOrtuna Online</ref><ref>[https://www.fortuna-online.nl/glenn-daniels-tekent-bij/ Glenn Daniels tekent bij] Fortuna Online</ref><ref>[https://www.fortuna-online.nl/glenn-daniels-op-proef/ Glenn Daniels op proef] Fortuna Online</ref>\n|caps4= 1\n|goals4= 0\n|years5= 2016-2017\n|clubs5= [[Sporting Hasselt]]<ref name=\"fortuna\"/>\n|caps5= 17\n|goals5= 0\n|years6= 2017-2019<ref>[https://www.voetbalbelgie.be/voetbalnieuws/tien-spelers-verlaten-lommel-sk-deze-zomer/2019/05/02/ Tien spelers verlaten Lommel SK deze zomer] Voetbalbelgie.be</ref>\n|clubs6= [[Lommel S.K.]]<ref>[https://www.internetgaz